titles.title: A joint resolution providing for the reappointment of Walter E. Massey as a citizen regent of the Board of Regents of the Smithsonian Institution.

action.text: Read twice and referred to the Committee on Rules and Administration.

bill.summary:
3/8/2007--Introduced.
Reappoints Walter E. Massey as a citizen regent of the Board of Regents of the Smithsonian Institution.
